Package model

Class Project

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Project
  • public class Project
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class is to create the projects of the company with specify attributes: Project Name Planed Start Date Planed Final Date Budget Identification code Its assigned project manager The client The duration of each predefined stage: "START", "ANALYSIS", "DESIGN", "EXECUTION", "CLOSE", "TRACING", "PROYECC CONTROL"
